notes: Ponting was dropped by VVS Laxman at first slip on 0. Australia were 16 for 1 from 2.4 overs. Agarkar was the bowler
Hayden dropped on 9 by Laxman at point. Australia were 18 for 1 in 5.4 overs. The bowler was Zaheer Khan
Hayden was dropped by Harbhajan at square leg on 14. Australia were 27 for 1 in 6.2 overs. The bowler was Agarkar
Ponting was dropped by VVS Laxman at first slip on 36. Australia were 112 for 1 from 22.3 overs. Kartik was the bowler
Bevan was dropped by VVS Laxman at first slip on 6. Australia were 137 for 4 from 29.5 overs. Harbhajan was the bowler

stories.title: Winning when it matters
stories.subTitle: India v Australia, TVS Cup final, Kolkata
stories.summary: Ponting -- and the team he leads -- cares about just one thing: being on the winning side when the final ball is bowled

stories.title: The spin twins
stories.subTitle: India v Australia, TVS Cup final, Kolkata
stories.summary: Though the Indians failed to finish the job with the bat, their spinners once again proved the Australians' fallibility against the turning ball.
